cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.PL

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is a likely category as the paper discusses the complexity of model checking for temporal logical formulas in parametric Markov chains. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper discusses algorithms for computing reachability probabilities and expected costs in parametric Markov chains. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses probabilistic computation tree logic (PCTL) formulas, which are commonly used in AI applications. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper discusses families of stochastic systems modeled by parametric Markov chains. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper discusses symbolic representations of parameter valuations for which a given temporal logical formula holds.
